detaileddescription.para:
If buf is NULL , bufsize is ignored and only the number of available providers are returned. A typical call may look as follows: size_tnum=tirexDataProviderGetAll(NULL,0);
structtirexDataProvider*buf=(structtirexDataProvider*)calloc(num,sizeof(structtirexDataProvider));
tirexDataProviderGetAll(buf,num);
//...
free(buf);
